L, M, N, P = Data.L, Data.M, Data.N, Data.P
Kmm = tf.ones((L * M, L * M)) + default_jitter() * tf.eye(L * M)
Kmn = tf.ones((L * M, N, P))
Knn = tf.ones((N, P))
f = tf.ones((L * M, R))
q_sqrt = None
white = True
m, v = func(Kmn, Kmm, Knn, f, full_cov=False, full_output_cov=False, q_sqrt
    =q_sqrt, white=white)
assert v.shape.as_list() == m.shape.as_list()
pytest.mark.parametrize('func, R', [(fully_correlated_conditional_repeat, 5
    ), (fully_correlated_conditional_repeat, 1), (
    fully_correlated_conditional, 1)])
